headline: 2 Reasons to Like ELV (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Elevance Health has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 12.3% to $328.40 per share while the index has gained 7.7%.
